name: Anime Aesthetic Duskfall Merge
description:
If you want to donate towards costs and don't want to subscribe:

https://ko-fi.com/DUSKFALLcrew

If you want to monthly support the EARTH & DUSK media projects and not just AI:

https://www.patreon.com/earthndusk

At the moment this should be all three versions of our Anime/Manga model, plus Tarot Card and Digital Vivid memories.

If you DO need the "Trigger words" wait about 24 or less hours and we'll put those back in, they don't always make a lick of a difference in prompting.

At present, I DO NOT feel or think or otherwise that any other model is merged in.

The images aren't as NICE as they could be imho, because i'm struggling with prompting for this one.

VAE's are optional because horror faces are not something that can be fixed unless you're prompting better, and we'll test this one more soon!
